      "created": 1773992174,
      "updated": 1773992174
    },
    {
      "id": "69bf299000000000005314fb",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774135697,
      "updated": 1774135728
    },
    {
      "id": "69bf299000000000005314fc",
      "text": " 自分の機種では3D画面が100%固まる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774135697,
      "updated": 1774135726
    },
    {
      "id": "69bf29a200000000005314fe",
      "text": "  通話はできる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774135715,
      "updated": 1774135718
    },
    {
      "id": "69bf29c600000000005314ff",
      "text": "  [MobileHackerz]さんに伝え済み",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774135751,
      "updated": 1774135766
    },
    {
      "id": "69bf29d50000000000531500",
      "text": "   motoは癖がつよいらしい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774135766,
      "updated": 1774135772
    },
    {
      "id": "69bf29e10000000000531501",
      "text": " [こえ部]を思い出す",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774135778,
      "updated": 1774143118
    },
    {
      "id": "69bf2a200000000000531503",
      "text": " [Clubhouse]を思い出す",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774135841,
      "updated": 1774135855
    },
    {
      "id": "69bf2b2c0000000000531504",
      "text": " 他人と通話する習慣がないし、隙間時間もないので多分常用はしない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774136109,
      "updated": 1774136136
    },
    {
      "id": "69bf299100000000005314fd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774135697,
      "updated": 1774135697
    },
    {
      "id": "69c738d30000000000ecdd78",
      "text": "[nyarla.icon]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774663892,
      "updated": 1774663892
    },
    {
      "id": "69c738d40000000000ecdd7a",
      "text": "\tなんとなくの興味はあるけど、インストールにまでは至っていない",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774663893,
      "updated": 1774664008
    },
    {
      "id": "69c738e10000000000ecdd7b",
      "text": "\t\tこういうのを見ると、どうしても普段かぶってるアバターをかぶりたくなる",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774663905,
      "updated": 1774663979
    },
    {
      "id": "69c738f60000000000ecdd7c",
      "text": "\t\t\tVRM 対応が成されてからでも遅くないかな",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774663926,
      "updated": 1774663944
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7392b0000000000ecdd7e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tまぁかぶりたいのは [VRChat] 用のアバターなんで[VRM]対応だったら自分で書き出すしかないけど",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774663980,
      "updated": 1774663997
    },
    {
      "id": "69c738d40000000000ecdd79",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1774663892,
      "updated": 1774663892
    },
    {
      "id": "69d31f970000000000e8c9f9",
      "text": "[ポポポ認証の五次元異空間ミョミョーンでピョマれ]のポポポが用意されたので、あとは[五次元異空間ミョミョーン]と[ピョマれ]があれば、あのセリフが言える[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775443864,
      "updated": 1775444221
    },
    {
      "id": "69d31fd80000000000e8c9fb",
      "text": " POPOPOの命名は[ぽかえり]のポで、ポポポのポではない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775443928,
      "updated": 1775444313
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3214d0000000000e8c9fc",
      "text": "  [カワンゴ・川上氏に聞く「POPOPO」制作秘話　名前のルーツはパソ通の打ち間違え「ぽかえり」の「ポ」にあった！]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
